description:
In the apartment Aspettando l'Alba there are :
a large double bedroom with double bed and sea-view window;
a large private bathroom with fully enclosed shower and hairdryer;
a kitchen with a sea-view window, well equipped with cooking utensils, oven, dishwasher and washing machine;
a bright living room with sea-view window, equipped with table and chairs, led tv, comfortable sofa bed for 2 extra people:
a private terrace with amazing sea view: with private hydromassage pool (the pool is not heated), a sun-umbrella, table and chairs for romantic dinners at moonlight!!!

Included in the rental price: wi-fi internet connection, linens, towels, electricity, water and gas consumption.
To be paid at the property: final cleaning EUR 65; air conditioning EUR 10 per day or EUR 50 per week; Tourist tax EUR 2,50 euro per person per night.
There is a free public parking area near the property where it is usually easy to find a free parking space for your car. Being it a public parking lot, it is not possible to reserve a parking space.

You will be immersed in nature and you can relax as you wish.We are at your disposal to best satisfy your requests.
Services:
Fiumicino/Ciampino Airport Transfer (payment);
Transfer to Termini/Tiburtina Station (payment);
Transfer to Guidonia Station (free).
TOUR: Rome/Tivoli/Villa Adriana.We are about 40min. from Rome ,15min. from Tivoli ,5min. from the Terme di Tivoli.We are animal lovers but unfortunately we can not accommodate them because we have four hairs.
